wiki.text:
'Lass' may refer to:

In 'fictional characters': *George Lass, a fictional character on [[Dead Like
Me]] *Lightning Lass, a fictional superheroine *Shadow Lass, a fictional
superheroine

People with the surname 'Lass': *Donna Lass (1944 - c. 1970), possible victim of
the Zodiac Killer *Szymon Lass (1977-) best polish inspector in B.T.S 'Other':
*Alhassane Bangoura also known as Lass, footbal player for Rayo Vallecano
*Lassana Diarra, football player for FC Anzhi Makhachkala *The Bonnie Lass o'
Fyvie, a Scottish folk song *Solway Lass, a two-master tall ship *The
Tullaghmurray Lass, a prawn fishing boat lost near Northern Ireland
* LASS is an acronym in the audio industry for 'LA Scoring Strings', a string
  sound library

'Lass' may also be:
* A girl or woman
